Red....

1239
02:04:16,949 --> 02:04:19,033
Take a look at this.

1240
02:04:19,994 --> 02:04:21,703
Oh, it's him....

1241
02:04:23,080 --> 02:04:24,998
Come on, boy. Keep walking.

1242
02:04:41,849 --> 02:04:43,141
Keep walking, boy!

1243
02:04:47,813 --> 02:04:51,524
-Call your boy.
-Run! Phillip, run!

1244
02:04:51,734 --> 02:04:55,987
