Well, l've seen it all now.

1251
02:06:10,271 --> 02:06:13,731
-What's he up to?
-Damned if l know.

1252
02:06:14,149 --> 02:06:16,234
He's giving himself up.

1253
02:06:16,402 --> 02:06:18,570
Keep in mind, he still has a gun.

1254
02:06:20,614 --> 02:06:26,035
